    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so you can expect a smooth, reliable experience from the moment you drive off. It's the perfect blend of dependable and stylish, ready for all your upcoming adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
