    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example boasts a linear power delivery via individual throttle bodies and a healthy double VANOS system. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the M Variable Differential Lock remains tight. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the precise turn-in these chassis are known for. It is a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle that prioritizes drivetrain integrity and performance over showroom perfection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
